\c 124 ccMurwiri waIsiraeri ngaarumbidzwe Rwiyo rworwendo; rwaDhavhidhi 1 Dai Jehovha asaiva nesu, Isiraeri ngavadaro; 2 Dai Jehovha asaiva nesu, Panguva yatakamukirwa navanhu; 3 Vangadai vakatimedza tiri vapenyu, Panguva yatakamukirwa nehasha dzavo; 4 Mvura zhinji ingadai yakatifukidza, Rwizi rungadai rwakapfuura napamusoro pomweya wedu. 5 Mvura zhinji, inozvikudza, ingadai yakapfuura napamusoro pomweya wedu. 6 Jehovha ngaarumbidzwe, Iye asina kutiisa kuti tiparadzwe nameno avo. 7 Mweya wedu wapukunyuka seshiri parugombe rwomuteyi weshiri; Rugombe rwadambuka, isu tapukunyuka.
